    "description": "<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>3323年，为及时排除极端心态可能带来的社会隐患，元与人类共同发起了元镜计划，创造了元镜领域与执行者。当偏执个体报名参加元镜计划后，他们的思想世界会被投射到元镜领域，转化为各种光怪陆离的镜魇。执行者的任务是进入镜魇，消除其中的镜念，从而引导偏执个体回归正轨，维护社会的稳定与安全。</strong></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在一次任务中，执行者拾受到重创，丢失了全部的记忆。在从头学习如何完成执行者工作的过程中，拾听到奇怪的声音正试图与自己对话……</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179370/extras/51345bc056d91f0e72649d7e1f485fc0.poster.avif?t=1770892675\" width=616 height=122 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179370/extras/51345bc056d91f0e72649d7e1f485fc0.webm?t=1770892675\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179370/extras/51345bc056d91f0e72649d7e1f485fc0.mp4?t=1770892675\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>使用“回溯”能力跃迁至你短时间内去到过的空间。</strong></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>回溯至对你穷追不舍的怪物背后的盲区，打它一个措手不及；或者穿梭于复杂的机关中，以巧妙的思路解开谜题。</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179370/extras/d819ab6a9c02e48153c5782639197c5b.poster.avif?t=1770892675\" width=616 height=122 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179370/extras/d819ab6a9c02e48153c5782639197c5b.webm?t=1770892675\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179370/extras/d819ab6a9c02e48153c5782639197c5b.mp4?t=1770892675\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在镜魇中，执念会化为强大的敌人。或是驾驶着巨型机甲破坏地面，或是能将你的视野变得一片漆黑，或是能分裂身体变换形状。</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>但它们都有弱点。仔细观察机制，利用回溯等能力见招拆招，抓住破绽力克强敌。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179370/extras/8faba180534c6e9aa5ecdf16b93de41e.poster.avif?t=1770892675\" width=616 height=122 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179370/extras/8faba180534c6e9aa5ecdf16b93de41e.webm?t=1770892675\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179370/extras/8faba180534c6e9aa5ecdf16b93de41e.mp4?t=1770892675\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏画面采用柔和而明亮的风格化渲染，从古代遗迹到现代都市，镜魇的多样环境总能让你耳目一新。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179370/extras/d373db548b1ba8d23604a1e6f9d35059.poster.avif?t=1770892675\" width=616 height=122 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179370/extras/d373db548b1ba8d23604a1e6f9d35059.webm?t=1770892675\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179370/extras/d373db548b1ba8d23604a1e6f9d35059.mp4?t=1770892675\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>搜刮Boss战利品获得主要模块；寻找藏匿在镜魇各个角落的次要模块。</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>从7类主要模块及变体选择技能，弹反，重斩或冲锋；装配20+次要模块作为特性，形成独特的战斗风格。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179370/extras/3e03b56fb9a9e86443656cad994cabf5.avif?t=1770892675\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179370/extras_big/3e03b56fb9a9e86443656cad994cabf5.avif?t=1770892675 width=800 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>扮演“执行者拾”，与同伴们一起在母板共同生活，进入镜魇执行任务，并交流心得。</strong></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>根据你在关键时刻的抉择，游戏会迎来不同的结局。</strong></p></li></ul>",
